An unfettered eidolon begins with 1 Hit Die, a +2

natural armor bonus, and the evasion ability. As an

unfettered eidolon's Hit Dice increase (see Evolution

Points, below), it gains additional bonuses and abilities.

At 2 Hit Dice, and every 3 HD thereafter, an unfettered

eidolon's base armor bonus increases by +2. This bonus

may be split between an armor bonus and a natural

armor bonus. Also at 2 Hit Dice, and every 3 HD

thereafter, an unfettered eidolon adds +1 to both its

Strength and Dexterity scores. At 5 Hit Dice, and every 4

HD thereafter, an unfettered eidolon adds +1 to any one

of its ability scores. At 7 Hit Dice, an unfettered eidolon

gains Multiattack as a bonus feat.

