returning from a night of feeding, a penanggalen's organs

are swollen with blood. In order to fit back into her body,

the penanggalen must soak for 1 hour in this vat of vinegar.

Once reduced, a penanggalen slides back into her body. If a

penanggalen is slain away from her body, the body rapidly

deteriorates into foul-smelling grit.

